The paper deals with the problem of estimating the reverberation time (T60) of an audio signal, which is a topic related to signal processing and audio analysis. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SD (Sound), followed by cs.SI (Speech and Audio Processing), cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.IT (Information Theory).
